Making

Meeeee! I am experimenting with mold making still, I MIGHT have found a way to make my own custom dnd...
body:
Guess

Who’s

Making

Dice!

Meeeee! I am experimenting with mold making still, I MIGHT have found a way to make my own custom dnd dice! My first tries with single piece molds were successful but hard to de-mold, right now I have a bunch of two parters sitting over night which I will play with tomorrow. As seen I also tried playing with pigments, but forgot that the resin doesn’t like powder being mixed into the actual chemicals. So that will be getting a retry later.

summary: Help A Queer Artist Pay For College
title: Help A Queer Artist Pay For College
body:
Hi my name is MJ, but most people call me Ink. I’m a nonbinary queer artist that recently remade here, so I’m not expecting there to be a lot of traction to this post at first. I’m a senior in college with one term left to finish their degree, and I’d like for it to be possible to pay off as many fees from this year as possible before I graduate. 

I have a job I work at on the weekends, but alongside that I have preparations for graduation, volunteer work, family commitments, among other stuff to do and it would really mean a lot for this debt to not hang over my head for the rest of the term. So, I’m posting my ko-fi here and opening commissions! 

My lowest commission price is $15 and I take my commissions on commiss.io, but if you donate to my ko-fi I’ll doodle you smth as a thank you. 

All of my commission conditions are listed on my commiss.io here

and here’s my ko-fi

Please share/reblog this when you can!

title: YouChannell: 2012-2013 Chapter Thirteen Illustrations
body:
Hey guys, I’ve been working on this series for approximately two years now (in book form at least). Here are all of the pictures for Chapter Thirteen.

This chapter deals with Group Time and when a joke goes too far.

YouChannell: 2012-2013 is a slice-of-life realistic fiction story of sixteen tweens and teenagers living in a group home in northeast Portland, Oregon, United States. Be it the transfer to public school, a kickball match, crushes on girls, a new kid in the house, and much much more, YouChannell: 2012-2013 is sure to either make you chuckle, cry like a little bitch, or just stare at the computer screen for hours.

Go on, check it out if you like, and I hope you enjoy: https://manicthemod.wordpress.com/2019/03/25/youchannell-2012-2013-chapter-thirteen-group-time-with-katja-schacter-august-11-2012-1030-a-m/

Guys, it would mean the whole world to me if at least one person clicked on the link and read!! And also, thank you so much for clicking on this piece!!
